    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.13)) - tmp)
    tmp = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.48) - wp.abs(tmp + 0.61)) * wp.cos((v0 + 0.65 + v1 + 0.36)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.33 * v0 + 0.18)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(0.53) / 0.44)
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.56 / v1 + 0.01) * v2) + 0.49)
    v0 = v2
